{
  "stem": "13471.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- when these sentences were read, it became clear that three people were going to be acquitted-- Schacht, von Papen, and-- and Fritzsche, I think, was the third one.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But von Papen-- no, no-- Schacht is the one I want to talk about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, von Schacht had been Hitler's finance minister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, I don't know whether you realize it, but there is quite a group of US Schachts.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, as matter of fact, Schacht himself was born in Brooklyn-- a member of a group-- of a family that had emigrated from Germany to the United States and then back-- emigrated back.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He, Schacht, was brought up in Brooklyn and spent, I think, the first 11 years of his life on the streets of Brooklyn, New York.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he spoke, of course, [LAUGHS] perfect American English, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, of course, he wouldn't admit to anything but-- but German in the court.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was a smart apple, and he figured out in advance-- well before the end of the war-- what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so he went around among the Nazis, and he found-- took all the documents that would incriminate him and destroyed them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGH] that's what everybody guessed, because nobody-- he wouldn't admit it, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- and he was free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, [LAUGHS] then he went downstairs to the-- they have a little press room-- and they said that he would be available with the other guys to-- to have a press conference, you see, after--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the decision.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the sentencing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I went down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I took in the press conference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- the-- they had them, the three of them, lined up there on a long table, and microphones in front of them.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
